tamp": 1629122433, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2293801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 440507, "reply_to": 2293552, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 主要是心态问题", "timestamp": 1629124542, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295517, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 440507, "reply_to": 2293555, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 大概率能赚钱，但要做好亏钱的心理准备。如果要风险小，50%货币基金，50%指数基金，每半年或一年平衡一次，把二者比例调回1：1，即指数涨了就把利润一半放进货币，指数跌了就拿货币补充亏损的一半。风险会小很多，但收益也会相应减少一些。既要跑赢通胀又要稳赚不亏的靠谱理财不存在。", "timestamp": 1629164011, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2295871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 440507, "reply_to": 2295517, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 谢谢巴菲特，祝您早日干翻马斯克", "timestamp": 1629168522, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 440507, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "炒股/买基金怎么入门啊…😶", "timestamp": 1629116216, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1632034749, "url": "", "vote": {}}}